    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4454424>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Life stages of Protoplotina ambigua sp. n.: a) eggs in mealybug colony; b) single egg (enlarged); c, d) larva; e, f) pupa; g, h) adult." ;
